            </a>\n          </li>\n    <li class=\"gNav__item gNav__item--normal dn-pc\">\n      <a href=\"/privacy\">\n        <span class=\"gNav__item__inner\">\n          プライバシーポリシー\n        </span>\n      </a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"gNav__item gNav__item--normal dn-pc\">\n      <a href=\"/information\">\n        <span class=\"gNav__item__inner\">\n          情報公開\n        </span>\n      </a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"gNav__item gNav__item--normal gNav__item--fb\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61553735414491\" target=\"_blank\">\n        <span class=\"dn-pc\">Facebook</span>\n      </a>\n    </li>\n    <li class=\"gNav__item gNav__item--normal gNav__item--contact\">\n            <a href=\"/contact/\">\n              <span class=\"gNav__item__inner\">\n                お問い合わせ\n              </span>\n            </a>\n          </li>\n    <li class=\"gNav__item gNav__item--close dn-pc\">\n      <a class=\"drawer-toggle\">\n        閉じる\n      </a>\n    </li>\n  </ol>\n</nav>    <!-- /global navi -->\n  </div>\n</header>    <!-- /header -->\n\n    <!-- main container -->\n    <main>\n      <div role=\"main\">\n                  \n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/mail/css/style.css\"/>\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"/css/admin/jquery-ui/ui.all.css\"/>\n\n<section>\n  <!-- h1 -->\n  <div class=\"sub-h1\">\n    <img src=\"/theme/furukawa_consultant/img/contact/h1_bg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"imgObjectFitCover\">\n    <div class=\"sub-h1__inner\">\n      <img src=\"/theme/furukawa_consultant/img/contact/h1_item_01.png\" alt=\"お問い合わせ CONTACT US\" class=\"imgFit\">\n      <h1 class=\"dn\">お問い合わせ CONTACT US</h1>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <!-- /h1 -->\n  <!-- sub-container -->\n  <div class=\"sub-container sub-container--noPgLink l-container--w750 sub-container--contact\">\n    <p class=\"contact-leadText\">\n      弊社の業務やサービス・採用に関する事などのお問い合わせはこちらのページから承っております。メールフォームはもとより直接お電話よりご依頼いただくことも出来ますので、お気軽にご連絡ください。\n    </p>\n    <!-- 01 -->\n    <section class=\"contact-telSection\">\n      <h2 class=\"mod-hl-01\">お電話でのお問い合わせ</h2>\n      <p class=\"contact-telLeadText\">\n        お電話でのお問い合わせは<span class=\"important\">平日の8:30～17:30</span>までとさせていただきます。\n      </p>\n      <div class=\"contact-telNum\">\n        <a href=\"tel:0853215131\">\n          <img src=\"/theme/furukawa_consultant/img/contact/item_tel_num_01.png\" alt=\"TEL 0853-21-5131\" class=\"imgFit\">\n        </a>\n      </div>\n    </section>\n    <!-- /01 -->\n    <!-- 02 -->\n    <section class=\"contact-formSection\">\n      <h2 class=\"mod-hl-01\">お問い合わせ<span class=\"d-inlineBlock\">メールフォーム</span></h2>\n      <p class=\"contact-formLeadText\">\n        下記のフォームに必要事項を入力の上、<span class=\"d-inlineBlock-spNot\">「入力内容を確認する」ボタンを押してください。</span>\n        <br>尚、個人情報の取り扱いにつきましては、<span class=\"d-inlineBlock-spNot\"><a href=\"privacy.html\">プライバシーポリシーをご確認ください。</a></span>\n      </p>\n            \n\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n$(document).ready(function(){\n$('input[type=\"submit\"]').prop('disabled', true);\n});\n$(window).on('load', function() {\nvar getTokenUrl = '/bc_form/ajax_get_token?requestview=false';\n$.ajaxSetup({cache: false});\n$.get(getTokenUrl, function(result) {\n$('input[name=\"data[_Token][key]\"]').val(result);\n$('input[type=\"submit\"]').removeAttr('disabled');\n});\n});\n</script>\n\n\n<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n$(function(){\n$(\".form-submit\").click(function(){\nvar mode = $(this).attr('id').replace('BtnMessage', '');\n$(\"#MailMessageMode\").val(mode);\n$(this).prop('disabled',true);//ボタンを無効化する\n$(this).closest('form').submit();//フォームを送信する\nreturn true;\n});\n});\n</script>\n\n\n<form action=\"/contact/confirm\" novalidate=\"novalidate\" id=\"MailMessageIndexForm\" enctype=\"multipart/form-data\" method=\"post\" accept-charset=\"utf-8\"><div style=\"display:none;\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"_method\" value=\"POST\"/><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"data[_Token][key]\" value=\"d879ad69a98573488650b58bdfbc187e11a9256af4ee77595527471b6f557397dc6c054946b9d4d20613accbf4cb0ca5cffaaedb1dff8e96f81b6ebbb5d183e5\" id=\"Token529788036\" autocomplete=\"off\"/></div>\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"data[MailMessage][mode]\" id=\"MailMessageMode\"/>\n    <div class=\"contact-formBox\" id=\"RowMessageCompanyName\">\n        <h3 class=\"col-head contact-formTitle\"><label for=\"MailMessageCompanyName\">貴社名</label></h3>\n        <div class=\"col-input\"><span id=\"FieldMessageCompanyName\"><span class=\"mail-before-attachment\"></span><input name=\"data[MailMessage][company_name]\" class=\"mod-form-input-text--03\" type=\"text\" id=\"MailMessageCompanyName\"/><span class=\"mail-after-attachment\"></span><span class=\"mail-attention\"></span></span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"contact-formBox\" id=\"RowMessageCompanyRubi\">\n        <h3 class=\"col-head contact-formTitle\"><label for=\"MailMessageCompanyRubi\">貴社名（フリガナ）</label></h3>\n        <div class=\"col-input\"><span id=\"FieldMessageCompanyRubi\"><span class=\"mail-before-attachment\"></span><input name=\"data[MailMessage][company_rubi]\" class=\"mod-form-input-text--03\" type=\"text\" id=\"MailMessageCompanyRubi\"/><span class=\"mail-after-attachment\"></span><span class=\"mail-attention\"></span></span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"contact-formBox\" id=\"RowMessageName\">\n        <h3 class=\"col-head contact-formTitle\"><label for=\"MailMessageName\">お名前</label><span class=\"mod-form-hissuTag\">必須</span></h3>\n        <div class=\"col-input\"><span id=\"FieldMessageName\"><span class=\"mail-before-attachment\"></span><input name=\"data[MailMessage][name]\" class=\"mod-form-input-text--03\" type=\"text\" id=\"MailMessageName\"/><span class=\"mail-after-attachment\"></span><span class=\"mail-attention\"></span></span></div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"contact-formBox\" id=\"RowMessageRubi\">\n        <h3 class=\"col-head contact-formTitle\"><label for=\"MailMessageRubi\">お名前（フリガナ）</label><sp